Symbol.Script_3D:
! Combination Expansion Tank
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = -1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 ENDIF
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN END
res = 24 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN res = 8 ! Simple
IF useSysMat THEN MainBoxMaterial = sMat MATERIAL MainBoxMaterial PEN gs_cont_pen RESOL res
! --- HOTSPOTS --- !
unID = 1 HOTSPOT 0, 0, mainboxHeight-0.045*hh, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0, 0, -dTHeight-0.045*hh, unID: unID=unID+1
endRed = 0 IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 THEN endRed = 0.025*hhh IF endRed > A/2 THEN endRed = A/2 ENDIF
HOTSPOT 0, -B/2, -0.045*hh-endRed, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0, B/2, -0.045*hh-endRed, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -A/2, 0, -0.045*hh-endRed, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A/2, 0, -0.045*hh-endRed, unID: unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT 0, -B/2, -dTHeight-0.045*hh+endRed, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0, B/2, -dTHeight-0.045*hh+endRed, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -A/2, 0, -dTHeight-0.045*hh+endRed, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A/2, 0, -dTHeight-0.045*hh+endRed, unID: unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT -mainboxWidth/2, -mainboxDepth/2, -0.03*hh, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT mainboxWidth/2, -mainboxDepth/2, -0.03*hh, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT mainboxWidth/2, mainboxDepth/2, -0.03*hh, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -mainboxWidth/2, mainboxDepth/2, -0.03*hh, unID: unID=unID+1
! --- MAIN BOX --- !
ADD -mainboxWidth/2, -mainboxDepth/2, -0.03*hh FPRISM_ MainBoxMaterial, MainBoxMaterial, MainBoxMaterial, MainBoxMaterial, 4, 0.08*hh, 45, 0.02*hh, 0, 0, 15, mainboxWidth, 0, 15, mainboxWidth, mainboxDepth, 15, 0, mainboxDepth, 15 DEL 1
ADDz 0.05*hh IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 THEN CYLIND 0.015*hh, 0.0175*ww ADDz 0.015*hh CYLIND 0.11*hh, 0.02*ww DEL 1 ELSE CYLIND 0.125*hh, 0.02*ww ENDIF DEL 1
GROUP "cylind" ADDz -0.045*hh-endRed CYLIND 0.015*hh+endRed, 0.02*ww DEL 1 ENDGROUP
! --- TANK --- !
GROUP "tank" ADDz -dTHeight-0.045*hh IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 THEN CALL "MEP_m_Tank" PARAMETERS tankLen = dTHeight, tankDia = A, endRed = endRed, ringOn = 0, typ = 2, tankPos = 1, tankMat = MainBoxMaterial, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, res = res ELSE CYLIND dTHeight, A/2 ENDIF DEL 1 ENDGROUP
result_1=ADDGROUP("cylind","tank") PLACEGROUP result_1
KILLGROUP "cylind" KILLGROUP "tank"
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, cShow3D = 1, gs_ConMat = MainBoxMaterial, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show_3D = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConPosZ_1=ConPosZ_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = 1, ConPosX_2=ConPosX_2, ConPosY_2=ConPosY_2, ConPosZ_2=ConPosZ_2, ConLength_2=ConLength_2, ConEdit_2 = 1 END
Symbol.Script_2D:
! Combination Expansion Tank
PEN gs_cont_pen SET FILL gs_fill_type
unID = 1 HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1
DrawingNum = 1 IF DrawingNum = 1 THEN ! Top
! --- HOTSPOTS --- !
HOTSPOT2 -A/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0, -B/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0, B/2, unID: unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT2 -mainboxWidth/2, -mainboxDepth/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 mainboxWidth/2, -mainboxDepth/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 mainboxWidth/2, mainboxDepth/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -mainboxWidth/2, mainboxDepth/2, unID: unID=unID+1
! --- MAIN BOX --- !
PUT 0, 0, 901, A/2, 360, 4001
POLY2_B NSP/3, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen,
GET (NSP)
PUT -mainboxWidth/2, -mainboxDepth/2, 1, mainboxWidth/2, -mainboxDepth/2, 1, mainboxWidth/2, mainboxDepth/2, 1, -mainboxWidth/2, mainboxDepth/2, 1
POLY2_B NSP/3, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen,
GET (NSP)
PUT -mainboxWidth/2+0.02*hh, -mainboxDepth/2+0.02*hh, 1, mainboxWidth/2-0.02*hh, -mainboxDepth/2+0.02*hh, 1, mainboxWidth/2-0.02*hh, mainboxDepth/2-0.02*hh, 1, -mainboxWidth/2+0.02*hh, mainboxDepth/2-0.02*hh, 1
POLY2_B NSP/3, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen,
GET (NSP)
LINE2 -mainboxWidth/2, -mainboxDepth/2, -mainboxWidth/2+0.02*hh, -mainboxDepth/2+0.02*hh LINE2 mainboxWidth/2, -mainboxDepth/2, mainboxWidth/2-0.02*hh, -mainboxDepth/2+0.02*hh LINE2 mainboxWidth/2, mainboxDepth/2, mainboxWidth/2-0.02*hh, mainboxDepth/2-0.02*hh LINE2 -mainboxWidth/2, mainboxDepth/2, -mainboxWidth/2+0.02*hh, mainboxDepth/2-0.02*hh
PUT 0, 0, 901, 0.02*hh, 360, 4001
POLY2_B NSP/3, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen,
GET (NSP) ENDIF
! --- OTHER VIEWS --- !
ROT2 -SYMB_ROTANGLE * (DrawingNum > 1 AND NOT(SYMB_MIRRORED))+SYMB_ROTANGLE * (DrawingNum > 1 AND SYMB_MIRRORED)
IF DrawingNum = 2 THEN PROJECT2 -3, 90, 2 ! Bottom IF DrawingNum = 3 THEN PROJECT2 4, 270, 2 ! Front IF DrawingNum = 4 THEN PROJECT2 4, 90, 2 ! Back IF DrawingNum = 5 THEN PROJECT2 4, 180*(SYMB_MIRRORED), 2 ! Right IF DrawingNum = 6 THEN PROJECT2 4, 180*NOT(SYMB_MIRRORED), 2 ! Left
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, DrawingNum = DrawingNum, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, gs_fill_type=gs_fill_type, gs_fill_pen=gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen=gs_back_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConPosZ_1=ConPosZ_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = 1, ConPosX_2=ConPosX_2, ConPosY_2=ConPosY_2, ConPosZ_2=ConPosZ_2, ConLength_2=ConLength_2, ConEdit_2 = 1 DEL 1
END
Symbol.Script_1D:
! Combination Expansion Tank
EPS = 0.0001
! --- HARDCODED AND DERIVED VARIABLES --- !
mainboxHeight = 0.22 dTHeight = ZZYZX - mainboxHeight hhh = dTHeight/0.31 mainboxWidth = 0.09 mainboxDepth = 0.15 hh = mainboxHeight/0.22 ww = mainboxWidth/0.09
z = 0
